Description: The Fairy Tail are a group of powerful wizards. In this volume, the destructive spell, Nirvana, which has the power to change the good and evil emotions within people, is unleashed.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 17
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: Negi, the boy wizard, learns he will be teaching English at an all-girls high school in Japan, but he must keep his powers a secret.
Title: NEGIMA! MAGISTER NEGI MAGI, VOL. 33
Author: Ken Akamatsu

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 3
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Welcome to life in Ikebukuro, a Japanese city with lots of unusual activity, including the Black Biker, who is rumored to be headless.
Title: DURARARA!!, VOL. 1
Author: Ryohgo Narita and Akiyo Satorigi
Contributor: by Ryohgo Narita and Akiyo Satorigi

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 8
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Naruto, who wants to be a great ninja, is locked in a battle to decide the fate of the land.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 54
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: A mysterious disease has turned a high schoolâ€™s student body into zombies.
Title: HIGHSCHOOL OF THE DEAD, VOL. 5
Author: Daisuke Sato and Shouji Sato
Contributor: by Daisuke Sato and Shouji Sato

Description: More secrets from the past, in this world which echoes the Wonderland visited by Alice, are revealed.
Title: PANDORA HEARTS, VOL. 8
Author: Jun Mochizuki

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE SEASON II, VOL. 7
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Naruto, who wants to be a great ninja, must confront his inner demons at the Waterfall of Truth.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 53
Author: Masashi Kishimoto
